<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #2e6da4; color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 6px 6px 0 0; }
    .body { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 24px; border: 1px solid #dee2e6; border-top: none; }
    .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #6c757d; padding: 12px; text-align: center; }
    .btn { background: #2e6da4; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block; margin-top: 16px; }
    .entry-box { background: white; border: 1px solid #dee2e6; border-radius: 4px; padding: 12px; margin: 16px 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h2 style="margin:0">DOME Registry — Submission Received</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="body">
    <p>Thank you for submitting your entry to the DOME Registry.</p>
    <div class="entry-box">
      <strong>Entry:</strong> {{entryTitle}}<br>
      <strong>Status:</strong> Pending review
    </div>
    <p>Your submission has been received and is now in the moderation queue.
       You will be notified when its status changes.</p>
    <a href="{{entryUrl}}" class="btn">View Your Entry</a>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">
    <p>DOME Registry · <a href="{{frontendUrl}}">{{frontendUrl}}</a></p>
    <p>This email was sent because you submitted an entry to the DOME ML Registry.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
